<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nova mensagem de contato</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 20px; margin: 0;">
<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600"
       style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.05);">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f5e9;">
            <h2 style="color: #2e7d32; margin: 0;">📬 Nova mensagem de contato</h2>
            <p style="color: #777; margin-top: 6px; font-size: 14px;">System Home Pet — Formulário do site</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding-top: 25px; color: #555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                        <strong style="color: #333;">👤 Nome:</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #555;">{{ nome }}</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                        <strong style="color: #333;">✉️ E-mail:</strong><br>
                        <a href="mailto:{{ email }}" style="color: #2e7d32;">{{ email }}</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0;">
                        <strong style="color: #333;">💬 Mensagem:</strong><br>
                        <div style="background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; padding: 12px 16px; margin-top: 8px; border-radius: 4px; color: #444; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{ mensagem }}</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding-top: 25px; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8; margin-top: 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin: 0; text-align: center;">
                Mensagem enviada em {{ data }} via formulário de contato do site systemhomepet.com.br
            </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
